<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Walthasar, als wir nehst
                                                Hansen Steczman, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü ew geschickt
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der Erhart
                                                Wechslerin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, armen lewte
                                                  <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, den ir ir vihe
                                                  <expan>hingetrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, sagt uns
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser
                                                  <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> wie
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>gerin</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewte mitsampt im bey
                                                ew weren und ew <expan>sagt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, was
                                                und wievil des vihes ir
                                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, und
                                                  <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch das ir
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> mit
                                                  <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> eide behabt
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Darüber ir in das
                                                vor hielt und nicht
                                                  <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt, das uns
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew etwas unczeitlich
                                                dunkt. Nu hat uns die
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>gerin</expan> fürbracht, wie
                                                  <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vihes iren armen
                                                  <expan>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>nemlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dem
                                                  <expan>Czellmülln<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Czelle
                                                newn rinder, kleine und grozze, und
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Gerengroz doselbst
                                                vier rinder <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew und den
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hingetrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dasselb ir vihe noch
                                                  <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, als
                                                etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> antwurt.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                                  <expan>inve<ex>n</ex>c<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan>
<expan>cruc<ex>is</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
